Do keep in Mind that the Following Faq is NOT Completed.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1). Main Problems
(*) 3DNUS will not download any Titles -Make Sure that you don't have the NUS Servers Blocked.
(*) 3DNUS Crashes, and/or returns a JIT (Just-in-Time) error -Make sure that you have the latest Version of .NET installed, and Report the JIT error, and/or Dump the Log (If you downloaded a title)
(*) 3DNUS doesn't appear correctly, or is cut-off -Higher Resolution Displays may have this issue, but since the 2.7 Update this shouldn't be an issue.
(*) If you have any other Issue, please report it on the GBATemp Forum post -Do keep in mind, this Faq isn't completed; but will be in the distant future.
(*) If you get an Error saying that 3DNUS can't delete the Directory "\Temp" then -Cancel, and check the Option "Silent". This will ignore all errors, and will continue -to download all Titles and/or pack them.
(*) I get an Error Saying "Unable to update..."; what does this mean? -Make sure you have an Internet Connection, if not...connect! Another cause could be that the Update Info couldn't be retrieved, so try again at a later time.
